                  <stentry class="- topic/stentry " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\ntb\trident_ntb_ntb_overview.xml" xtrc="stentry:6;58:45">To describe at a high level what NTB architecture is implemented in the switch</stentry>
