         <p class="- topic/p " status="unchanged" xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\ntb\trident_ntb_ntb_overview.xml" xtrc="p:1;65:32">In Non-Transparent PCIe switch use cases, the switch may be divided into several separate virtual switch partitions. Each partition has its own USP and zero or more downstream ports. It allows the switch to be connected to multiple RCs. Each RC can only enumerate the devices in its PCIe partition. The NT EP provides an inbound Inter-Processor Communication (IPC) mechanism for the RC. The RC can access the other partition's PCIe memory address space through the BAR of the NT.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " status="unchanged" xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\ntb\trident_ntb_ntb_overview.xml" xtrc="p:2;69:32">
            <fig class="- topic/fig " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\ntb\trident_ntb_ntb_overview.xml" xtrc="fig:1;72:31">
               <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\ntb\trident_ntb_ntb_overview.xml" xtrc="title:2;75:38">NT EP use case within a Non-Transparent switch</title>
               <note audience="MSCCInternal" class="- topic/note " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\ntb\trident_ntb_ntb_overview.xml" xtrc="note:2;79:36">
                  <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\ntb\trident_ntb_ntb_overview.xml" xtrc="p:3;82:33">Source Graphics: <xref href="http://bby1dms01.pmc-sierra.internal/DocMgmt/getfile.cfm?file_id=440581" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\ntb\trident_ntb_ntb_overview.xml" xtrc="xref:1;86:42"><?ditaot usertext?>http://bby1dms01.pmc-sierra.internal/DocMgmt/getfile.cfm?file_id=440581 </xref>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <image href="../switch_management/graphics/trident_vep_architecture_non_transparent_v1.svg" placement="inline" width="6in" class="- topic/image " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\ntb\trident_ntb_ntb_overview.xml" xtrc="image:1;94:39"/>
            </fig>
